<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-29-1113 </DOCNO><TEXT>The availability of sufficient amount of energy is an essential pre-requisitefor comfortable living. Looking at different energy resources availableand present day energy requirements, it is clear that there is an alarmingneed for the development of new sources of energy, such as solar energy.The paper describes the potentials of solar energy, its prospective useand competitiveness in some solar energy applications. It is concludedthat the use of solar energy for power generation and water pumping ischeaper in the more sunny and remote area. The cost of solar desalinationand heating/cooling is also compared. It is emphasized that this sourcebe utilized to its full extent.</TEXT></DOC>